            <listBibl>
               <bibl>Winter JG, PMich III, 211, 1936 -- BL III, 111 (l. 1). - Traces of one line, which must have contained the address, are visible on the verso: at the end, one reads: p]ar[a] Ou[a]l[e]riou. (PH)</bibl>
            </listBibl>
            
